Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}依然無法入手, 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.07,0:22:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因戰鬥而疲憊的殖民地, 需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}If you do 不需要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}If you will 背後就交給你了
